client.gui.supplier

Class SupllierOrderPane

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.gui.supplier.SupllierOrderPane

  • public class SupllierOrderPane
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is for only one sub-Order pane that will be loaded to the main in Supplier Orders. Every pane and its actions that we enable for the user to do, will be handled in here and how we want to present every single sub pane will handled in this class.
